Welcome to War Dices Simulation!

This app is a simulation of the dices of war game. exactly! Red dices for attack and Yellow dices for defense.

It uses two classes: Dice and Wardice. This classes is covered by rspec tests.

Now, just use and have fun!


The principal program is diceshoes.rb
run it. 

The dice.rb file has two classes: 

 Dice -> simulate a dice of 6 sides
 WarDice -> simulate the dices of war game
 
Both classes are 100% tested. 
The rspec file is in dice/spec folder.
